
# WhatsApp Spam Classification – Week 1

## Course Code
902

## Assignment Title
WhatsApp Message Spam Classification – Text Preprocessing and Visualization

---

## Assignment Overview
This assignment focuses on preprocessing WhatsApp/SMS messages to prepare them
for spam classification. Each message is labelled as either **Spam** or **Ham
(Not Spam)**.

The objective is to clean raw message text and understand data patterns before
applying any machine learning model.

---

## Dataset
- Source: UCI Machine Learning Repository
- Total messages: 5,572
- Labels:
  - Spam
  - Ham

---

## Tasks Performed
- Loaded and explored the dataset
- Analyzed Spam vs Ham distribution
- Calculated message length
- Text preprocessing steps:
  - Converted text to lowercase
  - Removed URLs and phone numbers
  - Removed punctuation and extra spaces
  - Tokenized text into words
  - Removed stopwords and short words
- Visualized results using a Streamlit dashboard

